{"tid":1307203,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"面對喜歡拆 連儂牆嘅朋友","createTime":"2019-07-11T12:48:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T03:50:23.000Z","uid":275595,"like":141,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"31beb7ff9286f3dd90d5bd5aa4dbe18d269dd95b","tid":1307203,"uid":275595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T12:48:16.000Z","msg":"千祈唔好同佢哋拗。<br />\n<br />\n試下集體大叫<br />\n<br />\n勤力啲！ 咪偷懶 ！快啲拆！快啲拆！<br />\n<br />\n努力！努力！加油！加油！<br />\n<br />\n佢地拆曬之後就要大聲歡呼鼓掌！<br />\n<br />\n多謝合作！多謝合作！<br />\n<br />\n佢地一走，又再歡呼鼓掌！<br />\n<br />\n大叫好嘢又可以再寫過！<br />\n<br />\n但如果佢哋返轉頭，你地又唔好寫<br />\n<br />\n又開始大叫！唔夠乾淨！唔夠乾淨！ 拆乾淨啲！拆乾淨啲！多謝合作！多謝合作！<br />\n<br />\n以上口號可以無限輪迴loop。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n即使對方認為<br />\n<br />\nYou will never Win。<br />\n<br />\n「No. But I can lose. Again. And again. And again. Forever. That's make you my Prisoner.」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔想再見到你地再比人打。"},{"pid":"fb5abb35e473160b6695ed9f453a460035403d6a","tid":1307203,"uid":244243,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T12:48:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4aaa28f49b623cc4001abf5126faa4f9c944a2ca","tid":1307203,"uid":275595,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T12:52:36.000Z","msg":"咁總會有人想守，只提供建議，唔想再見到佢地比人打， 不喜勿插。"},{"pid":"dc8e1769c2c19e43ddcd71553f8e2c8b6763a20c","tid":1307203,"uid":270653,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T13:11:09.000Z","msg":"相信佢地係守住一個信念 只要唔硬碰唔受傷就得 同啲仆街鬥長命"},{"pid":"142afbc4eb05fdceed8c4cce45222bec40016636","tid":1307203,"uid":275595,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T13:12:00.000Z","msg":"一見到人想打人就走， 一定要學識保護自己才可以 繼續 抗爭。<br />\n<br />\n留得青山在， 哪怕冇得貼。"},{"pid":"82ff6710a89fd11cade86e9206c0e43653b2ff89","tid":1307203,"uid":272196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T13:15:03.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c1b7ebfa1ca21d163edd25631835cdd7044f6e2e","tid":1307203,"uid":276404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c